Interface BaseObjectConformable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseObject, CargoShip, Dock, Job, PassengerShip, Person, Port, Ship, World

    public interface BaseObjectConformable
    The basic protocol that every BaseObject must conform to. Contains several convenience functions that are used to pass data between objects
